{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99711-jia-ni-si-de-tangrenjie-zhi-xing","title":"贾尼丝的唐人街之行","description":"贾尼斯和奶奶一起出发到加尔各答的唐人街。和她一起探索这充满传统色彩的地区。\r\n","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Kalyani  Ganapathy"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99711-jia-ni-si-de-tangrenjie-zhi-xing"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117364/size3/f869de03a5e7e66d3b65f3e3ba6faaf1.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/117364/size6/f869de03a5e7e66d3b65f3e3ba6faaf1.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53932/size6/ce6764e56c5bd338ac76ffe9591096b6.jpg","text":"奶奶叫醒贾尼斯：“起来，贾尼斯!。”\n贾尼斯起床。\n今天是她待在刘奶奶家的最后一天。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53933/size6/6d2f86015bbe635eb3a9973cd992fb9a.jpg","text":"贾尼斯答应了居住在孟买的家人会带些手信回去。\n但她什么也没买！\n贾尼斯问道：“刘奶奶，您能带我去购物吗？”\n刘奶奶居住在加尔各答的Tiretti市集。\n这里也称作为唐人街。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53934/size6/a5cc06c282035ab59abed616ded39052.jpg","text":"贾尼斯和刘奶奶一起去探索唐人街。\n人力车在街上穿梭。 人力车的木轮发出咔哒声。 人力车的铃铛叮当作响。\n空气中弥漫着香气。","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53935/size6/8d40ebb80f547a21f41e7eeda53d5dc9.jpg","text":"第一站是李先生的店。“李先生 ，明天我就要回孟买。 我能买些什么当手信？”\n“这些紫色梅子糖果怎么样？”\n贾尼斯赞道：“嗯！这糖果又甜又香！”“我的兄弟一定会喜欢。” “我的兄弟一定会喜欢。”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53936/size6/9ae694046b4926379c41d4f3a13d7534.jpg","text":"6/13","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53937/size6/0a4635961189fe661eaf829b25ee6cfb.jpg","text":"下一站是陈太太的店。“陈太太，明天我要回孟买。我能买些什么当手信？”\n“这种黑木耳怎么样？ 在汤中加入一些黑木耳，会减缓流鼻涕的症状。”\n贾尼斯惊叹道：“呜！ 这看起来真像一个巨大的黑耳朵！。”“我母亲一定会喜欢。”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53940/size6/f4b79bb1830bc9f4e23281fc2c93b819.jpg","text":"接着她们去黄太太的店。“黄太太，明天我就要回孟买。我能买些什么当手信？”\n“这盏美丽的灯笼怎么样？”\n贾尼斯赞叹：“这盏灯笼的颜色是凤凰花的颜色。我父亲一定会喜欢。”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53829/size6/36ccaddc4a84e0ca36ecbdead0ac20d6.jpg","text":"手信买齐了，贾尼斯也饿坏了！刘奶奶买了饺子汤和包子。\n啧啧！贾尼斯赞道：“这个好吃。”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53830/size6/489cbffba1c9eeace800dcdb47d05830.jpg","text":"贾尼斯和奶奶停留在一座寺庙里。 寺庙里弥漫着焚香的气味。\n刘奶奶说：“当人们去世时，他们变成灵魂。我们启程之前，会祈求他们的祝福。”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53831/size6/491a179974e5334d98401ecc7783d9b9.jpg","text":"人们正在在大厅里的桌子打麻将。 麻将牌咔嗒作响！\n奶奶说：“麻将牌上刻着龙，风和花的图案。”\n贾尼斯说：“那比跳房子更加刺激！”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53938/size6/1d5b3b052259d1c1c28653ed66fbee50.jpg","text":"在回家途中，贾尼斯看见一位女士正在读报纸。\n贾尼斯问道：“那是华文报章吗？”\n刘奶奶回答：“是的！”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54000/size6/4c61adcad17200c4093ec90d8db52224.jpg","text":"“这是印度唯一的华文报章。只能在加尔各答找的到。”\n贾尼斯到了家，便开始包装手信。刘奶奶问道：“贾尼斯，你已经为其他人买了手信，但你会带回什么？” 贾尼斯回答道：“我们的记忆呀，奶奶，” “那是最好的手信！”","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":44}}